vote.title: A resolution accepting the FY 2022-2023 Annual Report on the status of Tax Increment Financing Reinvestment Zone Number Four (Cedars TIF District or District) and authorizing the City Manager to submit the annual report to the Chief Executive Officer of each taxing jurisdiction that levies taxes on real property in the District, and to the State Comptroller, as required by state law - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
